what we are.  Don't you know that? OK What is going on? Did you get 
hit by a stray phasar blast or something? You know, the war between 
us, the Maxitrons and them the Preditrons? Oh please! This is getting 
to be too much."  She started looked around and went to walk past 
WindLord. "OK GUYS! Enough's enough. I've had a hard day and this 
little prank is over. Get it! Over!" as she yells to the surrounding 
area.
